Usage: checkHierRoute [-help] [-outFile <string>]
                      [-ptn {ptnName | ptnNameList}]

-help                                  # Prints out the command usage
-outFile <string>                      # Prints the details of net-wise
                                       # violations in the specified file.
                                       # (string, optional)
-ptn {ptnName | ptnNameList}           # Report the nets that violate the
                                       # hierarchy with respect to the
                                       # specified partitions (string, optional)